videos.headline: Cuiellette's perfect pass gives Tulane the lead
videos.description: Tulane's Glen Cuiellette's pass just gets over the defender to hit Kendall Ardoin for the 20-yard touchdown putting the Green Wave ahead 7-3.

videos.headline: Memphis takes screen pass 46 yards to the house
